title: Thom Hartmann Program - January 24 2014
description:
January 24, 2014
The Thom Hartmann Program

Join Thom LIVE from radio row at Families USA - Health Action 2014 in Washington, DC today and tomorrow - it's all about health care and Thom will be talking with the people on the frontlines...Whistleblower Wendell Potter, Judy Waxman (NWLC), Phillipe Villers (FUSA) and more...plus, YOUR calls!

Anything Goes Friday

Hour One: Brunch With Bernie - Senator Sanders (I-VT) takes your calls
